headline: Amsterdam to Zhuzhou:  Cloudflare network expands to 100 cities
keywords: Data Center, Cloudflare Network, Africa, North America, Europe, Oceania, Asia
description: We’re excited to kick off Cloudflare’s sixth birthday celebrations by announcing data center locations in 14 new cities across 5 continents. This expansion makes our global network one of the largest in the world, spanning 100 unique cities across 49 countries.
